## BaДџД±mlД±lД±k HaritasД± вЂ” Phase 4: Calculator Module (NEW CHECKPOINT-13)

### Calculator Service Dependencies
```
calculatorService
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Uses: prisma.originCountry, taxRate, exchangeRate, importCalculation
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Uses: prisma.taxSnapshot (snapshot mechanism)
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Uses: prisma.vehicle.update (saveToVehicle integration)
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Implements: getFIFRate(engineCC) в†’ tax rate from 5 bands
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Implements: calculateImportCost(inputs) в†’ full calculation with taxes
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Implements: getTaxSnapshot() в†’ capture current rates
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Used by: calculatorController в†’ calculator.routes
в””в”Ђв”Ђ Called from: vehicleController.create (future integration)

pdfService
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Uses: PDFKit library (pdfkit v0.17.2)
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Implements: generateCalculationPdf(calculation: CalculationForPdf)
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Renders: Vehicle info, inputs, CIF, tax breakdown, final result
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Used by: calculatorController.generatePdf()
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Returns: PDFDocument в†’ piped to response

calculatorController (NEW вЂ” 6 endpoints)
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ POST /calculate вЂ” calculatorService.calculate() в†’ create ImportCalculation
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ GET /rates вЂ” calculatorService.getCurrentRates() в†’ active taxes/rates
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ GET /history вЂ” calculatorService.getHistory(galleryId) в†’ paginated list
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ GET /:id вЂ” calculatorService.getById(id, galleryId) в†’ single record
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ GET /:id/pdf вЂ” pdfService.generateCalculationPdf() в†’ download PDF
в””в”Ђв”Ђ POST /:id/save-to-vehicle вЂ” calculatorService.saveToVehicle() в†’ link to vehicle

FIF Calculation Engine (CRITICAL)
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Inputs: engineCC (0-20000)
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Rules: 5 tax bands by engine size
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ 0-1000cc: %15
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ 1001-1600cc: %18
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ 1601-2000cc: %22
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ 2001-2500cc: %25
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ 2500+cc: %30
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Formula: FIF = CIF Г— rate%
в””в”Ђв”Ђ Snapshot: Rate captured at calculation time (TaxSnapshot)

Tax Calculation Snapshot (NEW Phase 4)
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Captures: TaxRate + ExchangeRate at calculation time
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Stores: taxSnapshot record with calculationId
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Prevents: Historical rate changes affecting past calculations
в””в”Ђв”Ђ Used by: Calculator engine for accurate audit trail
```

### Gallery Tenant Chain (Calculator)
```
Request в†’ authenticate в†’ requireGalleryAccess в†’ galleryTenant в†’ validate(schema)
          в†“
    calculatorController.calculate(galleryId=?)
          в†“
    calculatorService.calculate(galleryId)
          в†“
    prisma.importCalculation.create({ where: { galleryId } })
```

